<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="M" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Mary" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Mary,</orth> name 1) of the Holy Virgin: <bibl n="shak. jn 2.538" default="NO" valid="yes">John II, 538</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 2.1.56" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 II, 1, 56</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 5.2.33" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 V, 2, 33</bibl>. 2) a daughter of Henry VIII: <bibl n="shak. h8 2.4.175" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 II, 4, 175</bibl>. 3) of Olivia's woman: <bibl n="shak. tn 1.3.57" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. I, 3, 57</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tn 1.5.11" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 5, 11</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tn 2.3.130" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 3, 130</bibl> (cf. <emph>Maria</emph>).
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>